          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sunshine on Government Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>Requires the Office of Management and Budget (OMB) to create a separate website with a distinct URL, apart from the OMB website,&nbsp;about the reports issued by each Office of Inspector General. Requires such website to include: (1) a general description of the role of the&nbsp;Office of Inspector General, (2) a description of the types of reports issued by the Office of Inspector General, (3) a list of each federal agency that has an Office of Inspector General, and (4) a link to a website containing Inspector General reports.</p>]]></text>
        </item>
